HEADWORD: Indispensableness
<hw>In`dis*pen"sa*ble*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The state or quality
of being indispensable, or absolutely necessary.</def> <rj><au>S.
Clarke.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

